                             The Dominion War 2
==============================================================================
         A scenario for the game "-Star_Trek-" by Frank Mathieson
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

+++ UNITED FEDERATION OF PLANETS
+++ STARFLEET HEADQUARTERS
+++ STARDATE 51216.4
+++ ADMIRAL V'ENGA

Dear Captain V. SAVIEUR,

the Dominion has sent out the Jem'Hadar to prepare invasion of the Alpha
Quadrant. Also some Cardassian cruisers have been reported to have joined
the large attack fleet.

The galaxy class USS MALCOM (NCC-1743) has order to defeat the intruders
at any cost.

Good luck, Captain!
