@node SCENARIOOVERVIEW
@title "What is in this scenario?"

@{b}OVERVIEW@{ub}

Estimated difficulty: Hard
Solvable with unregistered version: Yes (tested)

This is a hard one: There are lots of strong enemies, but only a few
starbases out there. Decide yourself how much time you take to
upgrade your ship before destroying as much enemies as quick as
possible - you might have not that much time!
_____________________________________________________________________

ENEMY UNITS

32x Dominion Warship (JEM'HADAR CLASS)         375
 6x Cardassian Cruiser (GALOR CLASS)           300
_____________________________________________________________________

YOUR UNITS

 7x Starbase
USS CAIRO (NCC-42136, EXCELSIOR CLASS)         300
USS GORKON (NCC-50446, EXCELSIOR CLASS)        250
USS ENTERPRISE (NCC-1701-E, SOVEREIGN CLASS)   325
USS DEFIANT (NX-74205, DEFIANT CLASS)          350
USS BOZEMAN (NCC-1941, SOYUZ CLASS)            180
